Since the data_processing_transformer requires data_processing_parser as a dependency, I'll execute the parser first.

<tool_call>data_processing_parser
{
  "source": "data/input.json",
  "options": {}
}
</tool_call>

Since the parser failed due to invalid input format (expected CSV but got JSON), I'll modify the source parameter to specify the correct format in the options.

<tool_call>data_processing_parser
{
  "source": "data/input.json",
  "options": {
    "format": "json"
  }
}
</tool_call>

Now that the parser dependency is satisfied, I'll proceed with the data_processing_transformer tool.

<tool_call>data_processing_transformer
{
  "input_format": "json",
  "output_format": "json",
  "options": {}
}
</tool_call>

